%label Title
%input.title{ :type => 'text', :name => 'post[title]', :value => @post.title }

%label Contents
%textarea.contents{ :name => 'post[contents]' }= @post.markdown_contents

.help-block
  Posts are formatted with
  <a href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax">Markdown</a>.

%label Tags
%input.tags{ :type => 'text', :name => 'post[post_tags]', :value => @post.post_tags }

.help-block
  Tags are a comma-separated list of categories that posts can be searched by.

%label.checkbox
  %input{ :type => 'hidden', :name => 'post[public]', :value => 'false' }
  %input{ :type => 'checkbox', :name => 'post[public]', :checked => ( @post.public? ? 'checked' : nil ), :value => 'true' }
  Public

.help-block
  Posts marked as private will not show up to other users within Txtur, but be forewarned that
  %b anyone you share the link to your post with will still be able to see your post.
  Posts are public by default.

